==韓國==
{{章節擴充}}
由於曾受日本統治影響，沿用日式公司組織架構，同樣《商法》（[[s:ko:상법_(대한민국)#제3편_회사|상법]]）規範「株式會社」（{{Kor|名=南|諺=주식회사|漢=株式會社|羅=Jusik Hoesa|附=助}}）<ref>{{Cite Web |url = http://taxsummaries.pwc.com/uk/taxsummaries/wwts.nsf/ID/Korea-Corporate-Other-issues |script-title = Korea, Republic of - Other corporate tax issues |work = [[PwC|PwC]] |date = 2016-12-23 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200213150554/http://taxsummaries.pwc.com/uk/taxsummaries/wwts.nsf/ID/Korea-Corporate-Other-issues |archivedate = 2020-02-13 |accessdate =  |deadurl = no }}</ref>，亦縮記「J.H.」、「㈱」（[[中日韓圍繞字元及月份|㈜]]）。<ref>{{cite book |author= |script-title=ko:大韓民國法制五十年史 上 |url=http://www.bookoa.com/module/book/book_view.asp?book_no=9418996 |format= |accessdate= |edition= |series= |date=1999 |publisher={{lang|ko|法制處}} |language=ko |isbn= |pages= |script-chapter=ko:2.商法 |chapterurl=http://www.moleg.go.kr/knowledge/book50yrHistory?jang=3&jeol=3&book50yrSeq=91 |unified= |quote= |title= |archive-date=2017-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116153959/http://www.bookoa.com/module/book/book_view.asp?book_no=9418996 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

